{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"7308e36e03","title":"中国共产党抗日救国十大纲领","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[],"tags":[{"id":"c20d333791","name":"关键人物文稿","type":"文稿大类"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wansui1","name":"毛泽东思想万岁(1913-1943卷)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"未知","files":"/books/wansui1a.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wansui1":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"687316b939","type":"title","text":"中国共产党抗日救国十大纲领","index":0,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"7308e36e03"},{"id":"53e94d722b","type":"paragraph","text":"（为动员一切力量争取抗战胜利而斗争）","index":1,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"7308e36e03"},{"id":"a0318cf9db","type":"paragraph","text":"《解放杂志》","index":2,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"7308e36e03"},{"id":"813eb7775a","type":"paragraph","text":"一、打倒日本帝国主义：","index":3,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"7308e36e03"},{"id":"6eec2f3680","type":"paragraph","text":"对日绝交，驱逐日本官吏，逮捕日本侦探，接收日本帝国主义在华财产，否认日本外债，废除日本条约，收回日本租界。","index":4,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"7308e36e03"},{"id":"5026445baa","type":"paragraph","text":"为保卫华北与沿海各地而血战到底。","index":5,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"7308e36e03"},{"id":"ff5b1c935c","type":"paragraph","text":"为收复平津与东北而血战到底。","index":6,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"7308e36e03"},{"id":"3b0f2971c7","type":"paragraph","text":"反对任何的动摇妥协。","index":7,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"7308e36e03"},{"id":"8ac191ff4b","type":"paragraph","text":"二、全国军事的总动员：","index":8,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"7308e36e03"},{"id":"af13df7f8f","type":"paragraph","text":"动员全国海陆空军实行全国抗战。","index":9,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"7308e36e03"},{"id":"4764b0f11f","type":"paragraph","text":"反对单纯防御的消极作战方针，釆取独立自主的积极作战方针。","index":10,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"7308e36e03"},{"id":"3297ec71c0","type":"paragraph","text":"建立经常的国防会议，讨论与决定国防计划与作战方针。","index":11,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"7308e36e03"},{"id":"c8414982c1","type":"paragraph","text":"武装人民，发展抗日的游击战争，配合主力军作战。","index":12,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"7308e36e03"},{"id":"173d0678b3","type":"paragraph","text":"改革军队的政治工作，使指挥员与战斗员团结一致，军队与人民团结一致。发扬军队的积极性。","index":13,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"7308e36e03"},{"id":"324db37eff","type":"paragraph","text":"援助东北人民革命军东北义勇军。破坏敌人后方。","index":14,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"7308e36e03"},{"id":"aed077567a","type":"paragraph","text":"实现一切抗日军队的平等待遇。","index":15,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"7308e36e03"},{"id":"563252609d","type":"paragraph","text":"建立全国、各地军区，动员全民族参战，以便从雇佣兵役制转变为义务兵制。","index":16,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"7308e36e03"},{"id":"0404c51c4d","type":"paragraph","text":"三、全国人民的总动员：","index":17,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"7308e36e03"},{"id":"5977d3600b","type":"paragraph","text":"全国人民除汉奸外，皆有抗日救国的言论、出版、集会、结社，及武装抗敌之自由。废除一切束缚人民爱国运动的旧法令，颁布革命的新法令。释放一切爱国的革命的政治犯，开放党禁。全国人民动员起来武装起来，参加抗战，实行有力出力，有钱出钱，有枪出枪，有知识出知识。","index":18,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"7308e36e03"},{"id":"8913934290","type":"paragraph","text":"动员蒙民回民及其他一切少数民族，在民族自决和民族自治的原则下，共同抗日。","index":19,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"7308e36e03"},{"id":"00120ab8a3","type":"paragraph","text":"四、改革政治机构","index":20,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"7308e36e03"},{"id":"3df3cbb0bb","type":"paragraph","text":"召集真正代表人民的国民大会，通过真正的民主宪法，决定抗日救国方针，选举国防政府。","index":21,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"7308e36e03"},{"id":"d629855b5e","type":"paragraph","text":"国防政府必须吸收各党各派及人民团体的革命分子，驱逐亲日分子。","index":22,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"7308e36e03"},{"id":"f7194caa47","type":"paragraph","text":"国防政府采取民主集中制，他是民主的，但又是集中的。","index":23,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"7308e36e03"},{"id":"88ccb240c6","type":"paragraph","text":"国防政府执行抗日救国的革命政策。实行地方自治，铲除贪官污吏，建立廉洁政府。","index":24,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"7308e36e03"},{"id":"642dadd68b","type":"paragraph","text":"五、抗日的外交政策：","index":25,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"7308e36e03"},{"id":"52bf255454","type":"paragraph","text":"在不丧失领土主权的范围内，与一切反对日本侵略主义的国家订立反侵略的同盟，及抗日的军事互相协定。","index":26,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"7308e36e03"},{"id":"bddd1edf3f","type":"paragraph","text":"拥护和平阵线，反对德日意侵略阵线。","index":27,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"7308e36e03"},{"id":"ce4d9c1e35","type":"paragraph","text":"联合朝鲜台湾及日本国内的工农人民反对日本帝国主义。","index":28,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"7308e36e03"},{"id":"25ed624466","type":"paragraph","text":"六、战时的财政经济政策：","index":29,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"7308e36e03"},{"id":"7ad8a3cae6","type":"paragraph","text":"财政政策以有钱出钱及没收汉奸财产作抗日经费为原则，经济政策是整顿与扩大国防生产，发展农村经济，保证战时农产品的自给，提倡国货改良土产，禁绝日货，取缔奸商，反对投机操纵。","index":30,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"7308e36e03"},{"id":"4596e23f6c","type":"paragraph","text":"七、改良人民生活：","index":31,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"7308e36e03"},{"id":"a871976d60","type":"paragraph","text":"改良工人农民职员教员及抗日军人的待遇。","index":32,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"7308e36e03"},{"id":"31671b2136","type":"paragraph","text":"优待抗日军人的家属。","index":33,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"7308e36e03"},{"id":"c65492f436","type":"paragraph","text":"废除苛捐杂税，减租减息；救济失业；调节粮食；脤济灾荒。","index":34,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"7308e36e03"},{"id":"c9265ffc8a","type":"paragraph","text":"八、抗日的教育政策：","index":35,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"7308e36e03"},{"id":"8564d384b4","type":"paragraph","text":"改变教育的旧制度旧课程，实行以抗日救国为目标的新制度新课程。","index":36,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"7308e36e03"},{"id":"94f3fe2947","type":"paragraph","text":"实施普及的义务的免费的教育方案，提高人民民族觉悟的程度。","index":37,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"7308e36e03"},{"id":"33f8b0dae1","type":"paragraph","text":"实行全国学生的武装训练．","index":38,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"7308e36e03"},{"id":"56498d9229","type":"paragraph","text":"九、肃清汉奸卖国贼亲日派。巩固后方。","index":39,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"7308e36e03"},{"id":"a2c4158014","type":"paragraph","text":"十、抗日的民族团结：","index":40,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"7308e36e03"},{"id":"30cf9fafaf","type":"paragraph","text":"在国共两党彻底合作的基础上，建立全国各党各派各界各军的抗日民族统一战线，领导抗日战争，精诚团结、共赴国难。","index":41,"publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"7308e36e03"}],"page":{"id":"0153abe3ba","publicationId":"wansui1","articleId":"7308e36e03","start":413,"end":415}}}},"__N_SSG":true}